        "subject": "LU-5957 mdt: Update MDT flags after layout swap",
        "message": "LU-5957 mdt: Update MDT flags after layout swap\n\nSwap MOF_LOV_CREATED flags between MDT objects after a layout swap to\nguarantee that layout will be re-created on next write if its LOV has\nbeen deleted.\n\nThis patch is backported from:\nLustre-commit: 1d3ee3ed2b56d73f392e1b2a033f7d274f5202d9\nLustre-change: http://review.hpdd.intel.com/12877\n\nSigned-off-by: Henri Doreau <henri.doreau@cea.fr>\nChange-Id: I37f09ba3f9d115bd6af79fb8c2cdd93ac5d11fdf\n"
